    "notes": "Intel GM45 ThinkPad. Fully supported by Libreboot (no binary blobs). First flash requires external SPI programmer (CH341A ~$5) with Pomona 5250 clip. Intel ME is neutralized by Libreboot's build system. After Libreboot is installed, internal flashing works.\n",
